      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions or equivalent analytical benchmark for rotating flow and scalar transport equations used in hemolysis model.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed against lid-driven cavity and pipe flow benchmarks; rotating impeller and power-law hemolysis scalar transport not verified against manufactured solutions. Gap remains."
